questions.quote: Where the hell is everybody? Bitter lady: Why don't you like me?! Chapter One: My first period.
I'm sorry. I'm staring. It's just that you have the most beautiful eyes.
Ooh! Look! Look! Look! Look, there's Joey's picture! This is so exciting!
Ross, you guys went out once. You took your kids to Chucky Cheese, and you didn't even kiss her.
Hey-hey guys, hey! How about we settle this over a friendly game of Fireball? Huh? I'll go unhook the smoke detectors!
So, as Joey's friends, is there anything that you guys think our readers ought to know?
Ooooh! Honey, well we'll find you something. Do you wanna wear my black jacket?
You had no right coming down to my office Ross. You do not bring a picnic basket to somebody's work! Unless maybe they were a park ranger!
Ah, look who's back! Why do you have bags? RACH, WHY DOES SHE HAVE BAGS?
Hey, I do it every week with three cameras pointed at me and a whole crew waiting!
